reviews.title: Phonetics
reviews.comment: I\'d give 4 stars if you could move to sd and 5 stars if you could show how the khmer word is pronounced phonetically in English. Audio would be nice too but one thing at a time! Good job, arkun!

reviews.title: Keep going Khmer
reviews.comment: Nice job! But one word with 2 or more than 2 meanings, need to be ordered or labeled its meanings by 1, 2 or 3 so the users will not get confused. How to sound the word. I give you 4.9 ~ 5, just fill users request and you\'ll get one more 9.
